JOB NAME:  IdsDrugRvrslSeq

DESCRIPTION: Create reversals for CLM, CLM_LN, CLM_REMIT_HIST and DRUG_CLM for drug claims

CALLED BY:  ArgusDrugMnthlyCntl, ArgusDrugCntl and PCSDrugCntl


INPUTS: See \"Parameters\" tab
              UV LoadDates Entry:  None
              UV RunDate Entry:     None
               

EMAIL FILES:  None


PROCESSING:   create reversal table and then process reversals

UNIX SCRIPTS USED:  None


DATABASE TABLES USED:
                 Job  Name                  Database                    Table Name
                 ----------------------------       ----------------------------       ---------------------------------------------------------------------
                                                    IDS_PROD

BCBSKC TRANSFORMS/ROUTINES USED: 


HASH FILES: None


OUTPUTS:  
                 Job  Name                     Table Data Created
                 ----------------------------           -----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
                 IdsDrugRvrslBuild          W_CLM_RVRSL
                 IdsDrugRvrslExtr            CLM, CLM_LN, CLM_REMIT_HIST and DRUG_CLM

RERUN INFORMATION: 
             PREVIOUS RUN SUCCESSFUL:   Reset the UV RUN_CYCLE entry \"EdwMemberRunCycle\" to the previous value if needed. 
             PREVIOUS RUN ABORTED:         Nothing to reset, just restart.

MODIFICATIONS:
